Make sure to scan the barcode on each item clearly. If the scanner does not beep, the item has not been added to your virtual cart on the screen.
I always feel a bit of pressure when there is a long queue behind me at the self-checkout. I try to scan my items as quickly as possible.
After paying, please remember to take your receipt from the slot below the screen. You might need to scan the barcode on the receipt to open the exit gate.
The machine has a contactless payment reader, so I can just tap my phone using Apple Pay. It is incredibly convenient and I do not have to touch buttons.
