Because the oven was preheated, the cake baked evenly. Therefore, proper preparation is essential for good results. If it wasn't preheated, the cake might fail.
Because the oven was preheated, the cake baked perfectly. If it hadn't been hot enough, the cake would have sunk. Therefore, always follow recipe instructions carefully.
If you communicate clearly, misunderstandings are less likely to occur. Therefore, effective communication is vital for smooth interactions. Because vague language causes confusion, be precise.
