Is it possible to pay the security deposit using a debit card instead of a credit card? I prefer not to use my credit limit for these types of travel rental holds.
I am traveling for business and need to ensure the security deposit receipt is itemized correctly. Can you provide a document showing the specific hold amount for my expense report files?
Is it worth paying a premium to rent from a major company at the airport? Sometimes the convenience of being right at the terminal is worth more than the savings from off-site agencies.
I checked the hidden fees for both companies, and the budget one adds a cleaning fee upon return. The premium company includes cleaning in the price, so it is actually cheaper overall.
I noticed that one of the hubcaps is missing from the rear wheel. Should I report this to the manager, or is it already noted in your system records?
