I am checking the door hinges to ensure they open and close smoothly without any squeaking noises. It is important that everything feels solid and reliable for my rental.
Are there any issues with the tires that I should be aware of? I want to ensure the tread is sufficient and that there are no visible cuts on the sidewalls.
