Roundabouts are quite common in this region, and they can be confusing for drivers who are not used to them. Always yield to the traffic already inside the circle before entering.
I noticed that many drivers here do not use their turn signals. I must stay alert and maintain a safe distance from other cars to react quickly to any sudden maneuvers.
