We are bringing a pet crate in the trunk. Does this car have a low bumper height to make it easier for our large dog to jump inside comfortably and safely?
I am traveling for business and need to transport trade show displays. Is there a cargo van available that offers enough vertical height for my tall demonstration materials and boxes?
I notice that your license is a learner's permit. Unfortunately, our company policy requires a full, unrestricted driver's license to qualify for a vehicle rental at any of our branches.
Is there anyone else who will be driving the car? We must validate the driver's license of every additional driver to ensure they are covered by our comprehensive insurance policy protection.
Your license check is complete, and we are ready to proceed with the payment process. Would you like to add any additional protection plans to your rental package before finishing today?
Thank you for the warm welcome. Could you please explain how the valet parking service works and where I should leave my car keys tonight?
What is the policy for late check-out? I have a late flight and I would really appreciate it if I could stay in my room until two.
Excuse me, I am checking in as part of a conference group. The reservation was made by my company, so I believe everything should already be paid for in advance today.
I would like to arrange for a wake-up call tomorrow morning at seven o'clock. Is that something you can set up for me right now at the front desk here?
I would like to request an extra turn-down service for my room this evening. Please ensure that the bed is made neatly and that fresh towels are provided for my stay.
Is it possible to have my bed made with extra pillows today? I had a long flight and I would really appreciate a very comfortable sleeping arrangement this coming night.
Could you please arrange for the bed to be made? I prefer to have it done during the afternoon hours while I am out enjoying the city sights nearby today.
I apologize for the trouble, but could you please have the bed made in my room? It seems it was missed during the morning rounds by the housekeeping staff today.
My bed was not made this morning when the staff came through. Could you please send someone up to fix it? I would be very grateful for your quick assistance.
I am staying for a week and would like to request daily bed making services. Please make sure the pillows are fluffed and the duvet is straightened perfectly today.
Could you please tell the housekeeping department to make my bed? I am leaving the room now and will be back late, so anytime before six would be great.
Good morning, I would like to request housekeeping services for my room. Specifically, could you please make sure the bed is neatly made and the pillows are fluffed properly today?
Could I please request a special turn-down service? I would like the bed made and perhaps some chocolates left on the pillow if that is part of your hotel policy.
Could you please make sure my bed is made with the decorative shams I saw in the closet? I want the room to look nice for my guest arriving later.
I am feeling quite hungry and decided to order room service. Could I please have a club sandwich with extra fries and a cold bottle of water sent to room 402?
I need to cancel my room service order because I have decided to go out for dinner instead. I hope it is not too late to stop the kitchen.
Hello, I am calling from room three hundred and five. I would like to order a club sandwich and a large bottle of sparkling water delivered to my room right now.
Excuse me, I ordered a pasta dish twenty minutes ago but it has not arrived yet. Could you please check the status of my order with the kitchen for me?
I am not feeling very well today and would prefer to stay in bed. Could you please bring me some hot chicken soup and a pot of herbal tea?
I would like to pay for my room service order by charging it directly to my room bill. Is that possible, or do I need to pay with a credit card?
Could I please get a pot of decaffeinated coffee and two cups delivered to my room? I have a guest coming over and we would like to have a drink.
The housekeeping staff missed our room today. Could you please send someone up with some clean towels? We really need to shower before we head out for our evening plans.
Excuse me, I am calling because we need more towels in our room. We have been here for three days and we haven't received any fresh ones yet today.
Hello, front desk? This is room five hundred and ten. I am requesting a few extra hand towels and a bath mat because the ones currently in the room are wet.
Excuse me, I am in room nine hundred and two. We seem to have run out of clean towels. Could you please send a staff member up with some replacements quickly?
Hello, this is room four hundred and forty. We would like to request a set of fresh towels as ours have not been replaced during the daily room cleaning service today.
Hi, I am staying in room two hundred and twenty-two. My wife and I need some fresh towels for the morning. Could you please have housekeeping bring them to our room?
Hello, this is room one hundred and fifty. We are checking out tomorrow but need fresh towels for tonight. Could you please arrange for someone to bring them up now?
Excuse me, I am in room seven hundred and seven. We have spilled water in the bathroom and need extra towels to clean it up. Can you send some immediately?
Hello, front desk? This is room five hundred and one. We require a few extra towels for the spa. Could you please send them up to our floor right now?
Excuse me, I just arrived in my room but I am having trouble connecting to the hotel internet. Could you please tell me what the password for the Wi-Fi is?
I forgot to bring my ethernet cable. Does the hotel provide them for guests who prefer a wired connection over the wireless network for better speed and stability today?
Excuse me, I just arrived and I am trying to connect to the hotel internet. Could you please tell me what the password is for the guest Wi-Fi network?
Excuse me, the remote control for the television is missing its back cover and the batteries keep falling out. Could you please bring me a replacement remote for my room?
Hello, I am reporting that the toilet in my room is constantly running. It makes a continuous flushing noise which is quite loud and likely wasting a lot of water.
Good morning, the telephone in my room is dead. There is no dial tone when I pick up the receiver, so I am unable to call the front desk for assistance.
Hi, the mirror in the bathroom is loose and wobbles when I touch it. I am afraid it might fall off the wall, so could you please have it secured?
Excuse me, the USB charging port integrated into the headboard is not charging my phone. It seems like the connection inside the port might be damaged or broken entirely.
Hello, I am reporting a problem with the sink faucet. It is very difficult to turn the handle and it drips constantly even when I close it as tightly as possible.
There is no hot water coming out of the tap in my sink. I have let it run for a long time but it remains cold. Please look into this issue.
The wake-up call service was prompt and reliable. It helped me get to my meeting on time. I am very happy with the efficiency of your hotel support services.
My room does not have any slippers available. Could someone from housekeeping drop off a pair of disposable slippers? I prefer not to walk barefoot on the hotel room floor.
Excuse me, I just checked into my room, but I noticed there are not enough towels. Could you please send up two extra bath towels for me and my partner?
I am in room six hundred and six. Could you please send up a shoe horn? I am having trouble putting on my dress shoes and this would be very helpful.
Could you please send up some extra tea bags for the kettle? I really enjoy having a cup of tea before I go to bed and I have run out completely.
I am in room eight hundred and eight. Could you please send up an extra ice bucket? I am hosting a small gathering and the current one is not large enough.
Could you point me toward the valet parking area? I have left my car with the attendant and I need to retrieve a forgotten item from the trunk today.
Excuse me, I just wanted to verify the breakfast hours. Are they the same for all guests, or are there different times for the club level lounge?
Is there a specific time when the breakfast buffet is cleared away? I would appreciate knowing the closing hours so I can arrive well before the staff finishes cleaning up.
Excuse me, I seem to have trouble opening my door with this key card. Could you please check if it has been properly activated for my room during check-in today?
I am checking out early this morning. Should I leave the key card inside the room on the desk, or is it better if I return it directly to you here?
The key card works for the main door, but it does not seem to open the fitness center. Could you please check if my access level is correct for guests?
Could you please explain how to use the key card with the energy saver slot inside the room? I am not sure if I am inserting it the right way.
My key card is very worn out and difficult to read. Could I get a fresh one that is easier to use for the door and the elevator access?
Excuse me, I am having trouble opening my door. The key card light keeps flashing red when I insert it into the slot. Could you please check this for me?
We have provided you with two key cards for your convenience. Please ensure that you do not leave them in the room when you head out for the day.
Good evening, reception. My room key card seems to have stopped working suddenly. I am currently standing outside my door and I cannot get inside. Can you help me with this?
Hi, I am calling from room 440. I accidentally spilled some coffee on the carpet. Could you please send someone from housekeeping to help me clean it up immediately?
Excuse me, I seem to have lost my room key card somewhere in the lobby. Could you please deactivate the old one and issue me a new card immediately, please?
Hi, I just noticed that the light bulb in the bathroom is flickering and it is very annoying. Could you please send maintenance to replace it sometime during the day?
Excuse me, the water in the shower is not getting hot at all. It has been running for ten minutes and it is still cold. Can you help me, please?
The air conditioning unit in my room is making a very loud rattling sound every time it turns on. It keeps waking me up. Can you send someone to fix it?
I am writing to express my dissatisfaction with the constant noise from the elevator shaft. It is clicking and humming all night long. Can you offer me a different room please?
The cleaning staff is vacuuming the hallway at six in the morning and it woke me up immediately. Why is this happening so early when guests are still trying to sleep?
The ventilation fan in the bathroom is vibrating against the wall and making a constant buzzing sound. It is very hard to ignore. Is there a way to turn it off?
The sound of the heavy rain against the thin roof is very loud, but the mechanical humming from the roof unit is even worse. Can you please check the equipment?
