I am looking for room five hundred and one. I believe I am on the wrong floor. Can you please confirm the room number for me so I can find my way correctly?
I need to confirm the room number for my wake-up call. I am staying in room two hundred nine. Could you please set the alarm for seven o'clock tomorrow morning for me?
Please remember your room number is six hundred six. If you forget it, you can always ask any staff member in the hallway to help you find your way back to it.
