I am heading out for a walk and noticed the rain. Are there any umbrellas available at the front desk for me to take, or are they all taken?
I see that many people are using umbrellas outside. Do you have any available for guests, or should I purchase one at the shop down the street instead today?
Please review my bill one last time to ensure all the room service tips are included correctly as I requested yesterday evening during the meal delivery service call.
Excuse me, I am checking out. Do I need to return my room key card to the front desk, or can I just leave it inside the room on the desk?
Could you please assist me with my bags when I check out? I have quite a lot of luggage and would appreciate it if a bellhop could help me.
I am checking out. Could you please verify if there are any pending charges from the hotel restaurant that have not been posted to my account yet today?
Excuse me, I am checking out. Is it possible to have a late check-out? My flight is not until late tonight and I would love to stay longer.
Could you please print an itemized receipt for my company expenses? I need to show the breakdown of room taxes and service fees to my manager when I get back home.
I have dietary restrictions. Will the tour lunch options accommodate my needs, or should I bring my own food just to be safe during the full-day excursion tomorrow morning?
Could you please confirm the pickup time for the city tour I booked yesterday? I want to make sure I am ready in the lobby before the guide arrives today.
I need a quiet space to stretch. Is there a corner in the gym where I can do my routine without being interrupted by other hotel guests?
Is there Wi-Fi access inside the fitness center? I like to listen to my own workout playlists while I am training, and I need a strong connection to do that.
Are there multiple elevators in this hotel, or is there just one main bank? I want to make sure I find the right one for my specific room.
Excuse me, I am looking for the elevator that goes to the underground parking garage. Is it the same one that goes to the guest rooms, or is it different?
